Changes in motor function and quality of life after surgery in patients with 
pancreatic cancer.

Nakashima Y(1)(2), Kawae T(3), Iwaki D(1), Fudeyasu K(1), Kimura H(4), Uemura 
K(5), Okamura H(2).

Author information:
(1)Division of Rehabilitation, Department of Clinical Support, Hiroshima 
University Hospital, Hiroshima, Japan.
(2)Department of Psychosocial Rehabilitation, Graduate School of Biomedical and 
Health Sciences, Hiroshima University, Hiroshima, Japan.
(3)Department of Physical Therapy, Faculty of Makuhari Human Care, Tohato 
University, Chiba, Japan.
(4)Department of Rehabilitation Medicine, Hiroshima University Hospital, 
Hiroshima, Japan.
(5)Department of Surgery, Graduate School of Biomedical and Health Sciences, 
