European Journal of Heart Failure (published by John Wiley & Sons Ltd on behalf 
of European Society of Cardiology) and Journal of Cachexia, Sarcopenia and 
Muscle (published by John Wiley & Sons Ltd on behalf of Society on Sarcopenia, 
Cachexia and Wasting Disorders).

